name: TheIntelligencerDailyNews
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Experience the award-winning Intelligencer on your Amazon Echo! Get local news and information for Central and Upper Bucks and Montgomery Counties in Pennsylvania. Bucks-Mont news. Breaking and daily news. Groundbreaking local journalism. Opinion-leading columnists. All the coverage of life, business, community you expect from your local daily news site. Sports! Phillies, Eagles, Sixers, Flyers. The colleges: Temple, Penn State, Penn, Villanova, Rutgers… Plus our area’s high schools.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
